{"tid":2125956,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍絲出書唔敢用自己名 資深傳媒人身份被盜惹誤會","createTime":"2020-07-26T14:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T14:53:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d77ac2f4d6543ea415c8b7db91862450bb9055","tid":2125956,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/SIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FSIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLmSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=d81980a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FSIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY%2F&h=14b6926b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/SIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY/</a><br />\n<br />\n俗語有云：「唔怕生壞命，最怕改錯名」。近日有本深藍陣營所寫《香港顏色密碼》新書推出，本書由《亞洲周刊》、零傳媒同明報出版社聯合出版。作者除咗有撐警嘅專欄作家屈穎妍、有「前白宮發言人」之稱前新聞統籌專員馮煒光等，竟然出現「施嘉雯」三字。國際關係學者沈旭輝喺Facebook開post，轉載曾經喺明報工作17年、現時係電視台Now工作施嘉雯嘅回應，更大嘆唔少人誤會佢朋友係作者、要同佢割席，所以想轉載當事人嘅回應，還其清白。"},{"pid":"a68c783c5ea435e25bc618bec0a401e7349589b4","tid":2125956,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef29a8c480b44540051b5ab9de1b840eec42bc2","tid":2125956,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a68c783c5ea435e25bc618bec0a401e7349589b4","tid":2125956,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src